'''自大狂'''（Grandiose delusions (GD), delusions of grandeur, delusions of grandeur, expansive delusions<ref name="Corsini2016">{{cite book|author=Ray Corsini|title=The Dictionary of Psychology|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=3oyoDQAAQBAJ&pg=PT985|date=2016|publisher=Taylor & Francis|isbn=978-1-317-70570-3|pages=985}}</ref> 或 megalomania<ref name="Corsini2016"/><ref>{{cite book|author=Robert Jean Campbell|title=Campbell's Psychiatric Dictionary|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Vrlsos_O13UC&pg=PA397|date=2004|publisher=Oxford University Press, USA|isbn=978-0-19-515221-0|pages=397}}</ref>）是一种对[[财富|财富]]、[[权力|权力]]和[[天赋|天赋]]等过于关注的病态人格。自大狂对宏大和奢侈有特别的要求比如[[名声|名声]]、社会影响力和物质财富等，一般被认为是[[偏执狂|偏执狂]]的一种表现形式。

